Project Specifications

You  will write a SMS/Email Message Blaster which will have two tables.
This will allow multiple companies to keep track of their customers.  They can either email them or send a text (SMS) message, depending on which data was entered into the customer account.  Your program must:

Do all data entry (Add/Edit/Delete) on company/customers.
Send a message blast which will:
Email if boolean set to true
Text (SMS) if boolean set to true.
Log all sent messages to the messages table
You may wish to use the php mail library for the email.  There are several web services which allow sms services.

Project using:
http://www.freesmsgateway.com/account
http://www.freesmsgateway.com/api